items.name: EchoTranscribe
items.description: EchoTranscribe is a powerful cross-platform tool designed to extract audio and transcribe text from any video file. Leveraging the capabilities of PyQt for a seamless graphical interface and Whisper for state-of-the-art speech recognition, this software makes it easy to convert video content into text on multiple platforms.
